"{\"uid\": \"learningenglish.voanews.com-a-locals-worried-about-olympic-surfing-event-in-tahiti-7503995.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Share  Share  See comments  Print  No media source currently available  The Summer Olympic Games this year are in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999948390723, \"rank\": 5.16084277585124e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996691639357084, \"rank\": 0.0003060066259848929, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris does not have an ocean.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 130, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999948390723, \"rank\": 5.16084277585124e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, how do organizers plan to present competition in the sport of surfing?\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are taking that Olympic event halfway around the world to the South Pacific country of French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes will compete on the island of Tahiti, in a small coastal village called Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999998365224334, \"rank\": 1.6347765394389136e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The area is rural.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not even have a road until the 1970s.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of people are expected to visit Teahupo'o to watch the sport, as the surfers go out onto the famous waves from July 27 to August 4.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peva Levy is a Tahitian surfer.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999994512715289, \"rank\": 5.47945320761048e-07, \"text\": \"Tahitian\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the Teahupo'o beach was a \\\"secret spot\\\" when he first rode the waves there more than fifty years ago.\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, he added, it did not stay secret.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Teahupo'o gained fame among surfers around the world in the years since.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Levy said the place has a special energy, a feeling known as \\\"mana\\\" in the local language.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the people who live there want that special quality protected.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are concerns that a week of Olympic competition in Teahupo'o could destroy the \\\"mana\\\" and harm the environment that surrounds it.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Proposed preparations for the event included building temporary housing, roads, and even a large structure out on the water.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The work called for drilling into acoral reef.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Opposition to the plans quickly grew.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Environmentalists, locals and surfers joined forces to protect Teahupo'o's culture, its corals and other sea life.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was too much for us, a big change,\\\" said Levy, who also serves on a local environmental organization Vai Ara o Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Vai\", \"score\": 0.9530752511166547, \"rank\": 0.04643129567304413, \"text\": \"Vai\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Vai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Vai\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group told the Olympic organizers they did not want new buildings or roads.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And organizers are adjusting their plans as a result.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, they will not be building any Olympic housing.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, athletes will stay on a nearby boat.\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Homes of locals will serve other Olympic housing needs.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers also shrunk the size of the planned structure, a platform, they will build in the ocean.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Judges will watch the competition from the platform.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people worry that thedrillinginto the reef will disrupt the ecosystem and attract a dangerousalgae.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If fish eat the algae, people who eat the fish can become sick.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Twenty-two-year-old Mormon Maitei is concerned about the fish in the area.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2296, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mormons\", \"score\": 0.9321022805642835, \"rank\": 0.07187676118436256, \"text\": \"Mormon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mormons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mormons\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maitei is a spearfisher who catches fish to feed his family.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He sells what they do not need.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The water is \\\"where we get our dinner,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tahitians also worry that changing the reef could also change the shape of the famous waves.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2494, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.70774012778914e-28, \"text\": \"Tahitians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Levy said if the reef cracks and breaks off \\\"there will be no more wave over here, it will be finished for us.\\\"\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In December, the worries of the locals were confirmed when a boat working on some Olympic construction hit a piece of the reef and broke it.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cindy Otcenasek, the president of Via Ara o Teahupo'o, called the destruction deeply hurtful.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cindy_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9993580129511742, \"rank\": 0.0006402654450919111, \"text\": \"Cindy\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cindy_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cindy_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said in Polynesian culture, people believe gods and spirits are everywhere, \\\"in the coral, in the ocean.\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"score\": 0.999680271040828, \"rank\": 0.0003198312184053235, \"text\": \"Polynesian culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesian_culture\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ocean is considered to be our most sacred temple,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Otcenasek said the fish live in and around the corals, \\\"so if we break a coral, we break a home.\\\"\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbara Martins-Nio is a senior event manager for the Paris 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games Organization Committee.\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3266, \"end\": 3276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.824607000298025e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3289, \"end\": 3305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999961071842618, \"rank\": 2.0729310546048813e-06, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She called the accident \\\"awful.\\\"\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said Tahitians have a \\\"special relationship with nature \\u2026 and it was like a bomb for us.\\\"\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3372, \"end\": 3381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.70774012778914e-28, \"text\": \"Tahitians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahitians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the incident, Martins-Nio said, the relationship between the organizers and locals has improved.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic group is moving slowly and asking for more input from the local groups.\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3565, \"end\": 3578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Group\", \"score\": 0.999940182218958, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am Dan Friedell.\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Friedell adapted this story for Learning English based on a report by the Associated Press.\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3746, \"end\": 3762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999993836783768, \"rank\": 6.163198499821465e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"_______________________________________________    coral reef-n.a long section of material formed on the bottom of the sea by the skeletons of small creatures that is home to sea life and living coral  drill-v.to make a hole in something with a powerful tool  algae-n.a kind plant life that grows in water  awful-adj.something very bad or upsetting      We want to hear from you.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 4144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Would you go to Tahiti to see the Olympic surfing event?\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4161, \"end\": 4167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999998365224334, \"rank\": 1.6347765394389136e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}]}"